
SELECT distinct pu.nom, pu.email, pu.user_id, pu.login, pu.visible_planning, pu.couleur, pu.droits, pug.nom AS nom_groupe, pu.adresse, pu.telephone, pu.mobile, pu.metier, pu.commentaire, pu.date_dernier_login, pu.login_actif, COUNT(pp.periode_id) AS totalPeriodes
                    from planning_user pu
                    LEFT JOIN planning_periode pp ON pu.user_id = pp.user_id
					LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe pug ON pug.user_groupe_id = pu.user_groupe_id
					WHERE pu.user_id <> "publicspl" 		AND (pu.user_groupe_id IN ('')			GROUP BY pu.nom, pu.user_id, pu.login, pu.visible_planning, pu.couleur, pu.droits, nom_groupe
                    ORDER BY nom asc

                    from planning_user pu

					LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe pug ON pug.user_groupe_id = pu.user_groupe_id
					WHERE pu.user_id <> "publicspl" 		AND (pu.user_groupe_id IN ('')			GROUP BY pu.nom, pu.user_id, pu.login, pu.visible_planning, pu.couleur, pu.droits, nom_groupe
                    ORDER BY nom asc

                    ORDER BY nom asc

SELECT distinct pu.nom, pu.email, pu.user_id, pu.login, pu.visible_planning, pu.couleur, pu.droits, pug.nom AS nom_groupe, pu.adresse, pu.telephone, pu.mobile, pu.metier, pu.commentaire, pu.date_dernier_login, pu.login_actif, COUNT(pp.periode_id) AS totalPeriodes
                    from planning_user pu
                    LEFT JOIN planning_periode pp ON pu.user_id = pp.user_id
					LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe pug ON pug.user_groupe_id = pu.user_groupe_id
					WHERE pu.user_id <> "publicspl" 		AND pu.user_groupe_id != '5' 			GROUP BY pu.nom, pu.user_id, pu.login, pu.visible_planning, pu.couleur, pu.droits, nom_groupe
                    ORDER BY user_groupe_id ASC

                    from planning_user pu
                    LEFT JOIN planning_periode pp ON pu.user_id = pp.user_id
					LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe pug ON pug.user_groupe_id = pu.user_groupe_id
					WHERE pu.user_id <> "publicspl" 		AND pu.user_groupe_id != '5' 			GROUP BY pu.nom, pu.user_id, pu.login, pu.visible_planning, pu.couleur, pu.droits, nom_groupe
                    ORDER BY user_groupe_id ASC

SELECT * FROM planning_periode WHERE date_debut = '2019-06-20'AND duree_details !='PM' AND user_id = 'ANECOICA')
SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-06-03' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-06-03')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-08-27' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-06-03')
			) AND planning_periode.ressource_id LIKE CONCAT(\'%\',103341,\'%\')

		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-06-03' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-06-03')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-08-27' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-06-03')
			) AND planning_periode.ressource_id LIKE CONCAT(\'%\',103341,\'%\') ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-06-03' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-06-03')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-08-27' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-06-03')
			) AND STRING_SPLIT(planning_periode.ressource_id, ',') IN ('103341') ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-08-27' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-06-19')
			) AND planning_periode.ressource_id LIKE CONCAT(\'%\','03YE170',\'%\') AND planning_periode.ressource_id LIKE CONCAT(\'%\','103341',\'%\') ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-06-19' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-06-19')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-08-27' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-06-19')
			) AND (convert(planning_periode.ressource_id using utf8) collate utf8_general_ci LIKE '%Array%' ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-06-19' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-06-19')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-08-27' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-06-19')
			) AND (convert(planning_periode.ressource_id using utf8) collate utf8_general_ci LIKE '%Array%'

INSERT INTO planning_lieu (lieu_id, nom, commentaire, exclusif) VALUES ('CB', 'Carles Buenba', NULL, 1)
SELECT *, planning_user.nom AS nom_user FROM planning_periode  INNER JOIN planning_user ON planning_periode.user_id = planning_user.user_id  WHERE ((date_fin IS NOT NULL AND date_debut <= '2019-07-02' AND date_fin >= '2019-07-02') OR (date_fin IS NULL AND date_debut = '2019-07-02')) AND planning_periode.ressource_id LIKE CONCAT(\'%\','103349',\'%\') AND planning_periode.periode_id<> 218

			FROM planning_sample

SELECT * FROM planning_periode WHERE date_debut = 2019-07-04:00 AND (duree_details = 'duree' OR duree_details = 'duree') AND periode_id <> '217'
SELECT * FROM planning_periode WHERE date_debut = 2019-07-02:00 AND (duree_details = 'duree' OR duree_details = 'PM') AND periode_id <> '222'
SELECT * FROM planning_periode WHERE date_debut = 2019-07-04:00 AND (duree_details = 'duree' OR duree_details = 'duree') AND periode_id <> '224'
SELECT * FROM planning_periode WHERE date_debut = 2019-07-02:00 AND (duree_details = 'duree' OR duree_details = 'AM') AND periode_id <> '0'
SELECT * FROM planning_periode WHERE date_debut = 2019-07-02:00 AND (duree_details = 'duree' OR duree_details = 'duree') AND periode_id <> '217'
SELECT * FROM planning_periode WHERE date_debut = 2019-07-01:00 AND (duree_details = 'duree' OR duree_details = 'PM') AND periode_id <> '222'
SELECT * FROM planning_periode WHERE date_debut = 2019-07-02:00 AND (duree_details = 'duree' OR duree_details = 'AM') AND periode_id <> '226'
SELECT * FROM planning_periode WHERE date_debut = 2019-07-02:00 AND (duree_details = 'duree' OR duree_details = 'duree') AND periode_id <> '217'
SELECT * FROM planning_periode WHERE date_debut = 2019-07-02:00 AND (duree_details = 'duree' OR duree_details = 'duree') AND periode_id <> '217'
SELECT * FROM planning_periode WHERE date_debut = 2019-07-05:00 AND (duree_details = 'duree' OR duree_details = 'duree') AND periode_id <> '217'
SELECT * FROM planning_periode WHERE date_debut = 2019-07-02:00 AND (duree_details = 'duree' OR duree_details = 'duree') AND periode_id <> '217'
SELECT * FROM planning_periode WHERE date_debut = 2019-07-05:00 AND (duree_details = 'duree' OR duree_details = 'duree') AND periode_id <> '217'
SELECT * FROM planning_periode WHERE date_debut = 2019-07-02:00 AND (duree_details = 'duree' OR duree_details = 'duree') AND periode_id <> '217'
SELECT * FROM planning_periode WHERE date_debut = 2019-07-01:00 AND (duree_details = 'duree' OR duree_details = 'AM') AND periode_id <> '226'
SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-06-08' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-06-08')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-07' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-06-08')
			) AND ANY ( STRING_SPLIT ( planning_periode.ressource_id , ',' ) IN ('103349')
SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-06-08' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-06-08')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-07' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-06-08')
			) AND ANY ( STRING_SPLIT ( planning_periode.ressource_id , ',' ) IN ('103349') ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

			WHERE (0 OR planning_sample.sample_id LIKE '%hi%' OR planning_sample.projet_id LIKE '%hi%' OR nom_createur LIKE '%hi%' OR nom_groupe LIKE '%hi%') ORDER BY nom_groupe ASC, sample_id ASC

SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-06-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-06-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-08-09' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-06-01')
			) AND ANY ( STRING_SPLIT ( planning_periode.ressource_id , ',' ) IN ('103351')

		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id

			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-08-09' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-06-01')
			) AND ANY ( STRING_SPLIT ( planning_periode.ressource_id , ',' ) IN ('103351') ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id

SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id

			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-08-18' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')

		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-11-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-11-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-12-24' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-11-01')
			)AND ANY ( STRING_SPLIT ( planning_periode.ressource_id , ',' ) LIKE '%103349%' OR STRING_SPLIT ( planning_periode.ressource_id , ',' ) LIKE '%103349%') ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on WHERE planning_periode.ressource_id LIKE CONCAT(\'%\',' . val2sql(pr.ressource_id) . ',\'%\') 	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-11-03' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			)

			) ORDER by lieu_nom ASC
SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id

			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-11-03' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')

			) ORDER by ressource_nom ASC

		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00'

		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details

			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			)
SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
			WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			) ORDER by lieu_nom ASC
SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
			WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			) ORDER by lieu_nom ASC

SELECT ppe.*
		FROM planning_periode AS ppe
		INNER JOIN planning_projet AS proj ON proj.projet_id = ppe.projet_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user AS pu ON pu.user_id = ppe.user_id
		WHERE 0 = 0
		AND 
		(
			(date_debut <= '2019-07-23' AND date_fin >= '2019-07-23')
			OR
			(date_debut <= '2019-08-23' AND date_debut >= '2019-07-23')
		)
		 AND ppe.user_id = M120 ORDER BY date_debut
SELECT *
		FROM planning_user
		WHERE 0 = 0
		AND visible_planning = 'oui'  AND user_id = V890 ORDER BY nom

UPDATE planning_projet

			WHERE createur_id = ''cel''
SELECT pu.*, pug.nom AS groupe_nom
FROM planning_user pu
LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe pug ON pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id 	WHERE visible_planning = 'non' AND groupe_nom != '' ORDER BY groupe_nom, pu.nom
SELECT pu.*, pug.nom AS groupe_nom
FROM planning_user pu
LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe pug ON pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id 	WHERE visible_planning = 'non' AND user_groupe_id != '' ORDER BY groupe_nom, pu.nom
SELECT pu.*, pug.nom AS groupe_nom
FROM planning_user pu
LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe pug ON pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id 	WHERE visible_planning = 'non' AND user_groupe_id != '' ORDER BY groupe_nom, pu.nom

SELECT distinct planning_sample.*, planning_projet.nom AS nom_groupe, planning_user.nom AS nom_createur
			FROM planning_sample
			LEFT JOIN planning_projet ON planning_projet.projet_id = planning_sample.projet_id
			LEFT JOIN planning_user ON planning_user.user_id = planning_sample.user_id 
			WHERE planning_sample.statut in ('Received')ORDER BY nom_groupe ASC, sample_id ASC

SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			)
SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			) ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches
SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			) ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			) ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches
SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			) ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

			) ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id

SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			) ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			) ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			) ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			)

		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			) ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			) ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			)
SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-07-01' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-07-01')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-07-01')
			) ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

SELECT distinct planning_sample.*, planning_groupe.nom AS nom_groupe, planning_user.nom AS nom_createur
			FROM planning_sample
			LEFT JOIN planning_projet ON planning_projet.projet_id = planning_sample.projet_id
			LEFT JOIN planning_user ON planning_user.user_id = planning_sample.user_id 
			WHERE planning_sample.statut in ('Received')ORDER BY nom_groupe ASC, sample_id ASC
SELECT distinct planning_sample.*, planning_groupe.nom AS nom_groupe, planning_user.nom AS nom_createur
			FROM planning_sample
			LEFT JOIN planning_projet ON planning_projet.projet_id = planning_sample.projet_id
			LEFT JOIN planning_user ON planning_user.user_id = planning_sample.user_id 
			WHERE planning_sample.statut in ('Received','Departed')ORDER BY nom_groupe ASC, sample_id ASC

			LEFT JOIN planning_projet ON planning_projet.projet_id = planning_sample.projet_id
			LEFT JOIN planning_user ON planning_user.user_id = planning_sample.user_id 
			WHERE planning_sample.statut in ('Departed')ORDER BY nom_groupe ASC, sample_id ASC

SELECT distinct planning_projet.*, planning_groupe.nom AS nom_groupe, planning_user.nom AS nom_createur, psb.nom as statut_nom, psb.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, psb.couleur as statut_couleur, ps.nom as statut_nom_
			FROM planning_projet
			INNER JOIN planning_status psb ON psb.status_id = planning_projet.statut_bill
			INNER JOIN planning_status ps ON ps.status_id = planning_projet.statut
			LEFT JOIN planning_groupe ON planning_groupe.groupe_id = planning_projet.groupe_id
			LEFT JOIN planning_user ON planning_user.user_id = planning_projet.createur_id  WHERE planning_projet.statut in ('a_faire') AND ppr.nom != 'timetable' AND ppr.nom != 'holiday' ORDER BY nom_groupe ASC,nom ASC
SELECT distinct planning_projet.*, planning_groupe.nom AS nom_groupe, planning_user.nom AS nom_createur, psb.nom as statut_nom, psb.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, psb.couleur as statut_couleur, ps.nom as statut_nom_
			FROM planning_projet
			INNER JOIN planning_status psb ON psb.status_id = planning_projet.statut_bill
			INNER JOIN planning_status ps ON ps.status_id = planning_projet.statut
			LEFT JOIN planning_groupe ON planning_groupe.groupe_id = planning_projet.groupe_id
			LEFT JOIN planning_user ON planning_user.user_id = planning_projet.createur_id  WHERE planning_projet.statut in ('a_faire','en_cours') AND ppr.nom != 'timetable' AND ppr.nom != 'holiday' ORDER BY nom_groupe ASC,nom ASC
SELECT distinct planning_projet.*, planning_groupe.nom AS nom_groupe, planning_user.nom AS nom_createur, psb.nom as statut_nom, psb.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, psb.couleur as statut_couleur, ps.nom as statut_nom_
			FROM planning_projet
			INNER JOIN planning_status psb ON psb.status_id = planning_projet.statut_bill
			INNER JOIN planning_status ps ON ps.status_id = planning_projet.statut
			LEFT JOIN planning_groupe ON planning_groupe.groupe_id = planning_projet.groupe_id
			LEFT JOIN planning_user ON planning_user.user_id = planning_projet.createur_id  WHERE planning_projet.statut in ('a_faire','en_cours','fait') AND ppr.nom != 'timetable' AND ppr.nom != 'holiday' ORDER BY nom_groupe ASC,nom ASC
SELECT distinct planning_projet.*, planning_groupe.nom AS nom_groupe, planning_user.nom AS nom_createur, psb.nom as statut_nom, psb.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, psb.couleur as statut_couleur, ps.nom as statut_nom_
			FROM planning_projet
			INNER JOIN planning_status psb ON psb.status_id = planning_projet.statut_bill
			INNER JOIN planning_status ps ON ps.status_id = planning_projet.statut
			LEFT JOIN planning_groupe ON planning_groupe.groupe_id = planning_projet.groupe_id
			LEFT JOIN planning_user ON planning_user.user_id = planning_projet.createur_id  WHERE planning_projet.statut in ('a_faire','en_cours','fait','abandon') AND ppr.nom != 'timetable' AND ppr.nom != 'holiday' ORDER BY nom_groupe ASC,nom ASC
SELECT distinct planning_projet.*, planning_groupe.nom AS nom_groupe, planning_user.nom AS nom_createur, psb.nom as statut_nom, psb.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, psb.couleur as statut_couleur, ps.nom as statut_nom_
			FROM planning_projet
			INNER JOIN planning_status psb ON psb.status_id = planning_projet.statut_bill
			INNER JOIN planning_status ps ON ps.status_id = planning_projet.statut
			LEFT JOIN planning_groupe ON planning_groupe.groupe_id = planning_projet.groupe_id
			LEFT JOIN planning_user ON planning_user.user_id = planning_projet.createur_id  WHERE planning_projet.statut in ('a_faire','en_cours','fait','abandon','archive') AND ppr.nom != 'timetable' AND ppr.nom != 'holiday' ORDER BY nom_groupe ASC,nom ASC
SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE AND planning_projet.nom != 'timetable' AND planning_projet.nom != 'holiday' AND planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-02' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-09-02')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-11-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-09-02')
			)
SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE AND planning_projet.nom != 'timetable' AND planning_projet.nom != 'holiday' AND planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-02' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-09-02')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-11-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-09-02')
			) ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-11-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-09-02')

SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE AND planning_projet.nom != 'timetable' AND planning_projet.nom != 'holiday' AND planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-02' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-09-02')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-11-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-09-02')
			) ORDER by date_debut,tri_heures_taches

SELECT distinct pp.*, pg.nom AS groupe_nom, pp.nom as projet_nom, pp.couleur as projet_couleur, pp.createur_id as projet_createur_id
		FROM planning_projet pp
		LEFT JOIN planning_periode pd ON pp.projet_id = pd.projet_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe AS pg ON pp.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id WHERE 
		(
			(
				(pd.date_debut <= '2019-09-02'
				AND pd.date_fin >= '2019-09-02')
				OR
				(pd.date_debut <= '2019-11-30'
				AND pd.date_debut >= '2019-09-02')
				OR
				(pp.statut='a_faire')
				OR
				(pp.statut='en_cours')
			)
			AND planning_projet.nom != 'timetable' AND planning_projet.nom != 'holiday'
 ) OR pp.createur_id = 'ADM' GROUP BY pp.nom, pp.projet_id
		ORDER BY pg.nom, pp.nom
SELECT distinct pp.*, pg.nom AS groupe_nom, pp.nom as projet_nom, pp.couleur as projet_couleur, pp.createur_id as projet_createur_id
		FROM planning_projet pp
		LEFT JOIN planning_periode pd ON pp.projet_id = pd.projet_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe AS pg ON pp.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id WHERE

			AND projet_nom != 'timetable' AND projet_nom != 'holiday'
 ) OR pp.createur_id = 'ADM' GROUP BY pp.nom, pp.projet_id
		ORDER BY pg.nom, pp.nom

SELECT distinct pp.*, pg.nom AS groupe_nom, pp.nom as projet_nom, pp.couleur as projet_couleur, pp.createur_id as projet_createur_id
		FROM planning_projet pp
		LEFT JOIN planning_periode pd ON pp.projet_id = pd.projet_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe AS pg ON pp.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id WHERE 
		(
			planning_projet.nom != 'timetable' AND planning_projet.nom != 'holiday' AND
			(
				(pd.date_debut <= '2019-09-02'
				AND pd.date_fin >= '2019-09-02')
				OR
				(pd.date_debut <= '2019-11-30'
				AND pd.date_debut >= '2019-09-02')
				OR
				(pp.statut='a_faire')
				OR
				(pp.statut='en_cours')
			)
 ) OR pp.createur_id = 'ADM' GROUP BY pp.nom, pp.projet_id
		ORDER BY pg.nom, pp.nom
SELECT distinct pp.*, pg.nom AS groupe_nom, pp.nom as projet_nom, pp.couleur as projet_couleur, pp.createur_id as projet_createur_id
		FROM planning_projet pp
		LEFT JOIN planning_periode pd ON pp.projet_id = pd.projet_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe AS pg ON pp.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id WHERE 
		(
			planning_projet.nom != 'timetable' AND planning_projet.nom != 'holiday' AND
			(
				(pd.date_debut <= '2019-09-02'
				AND pd.date_fin >= '2019-09-02')
				OR
				(pd.date_debut <= '2019-11-30'
				AND pd.date_debut >= '2019-09-02')
				OR
				(pp.statut='a_faire')
				OR
				(pp.statut='en_cours')
			)
 ) OR pp.createur_id = 'ADM' GROUP BY pp.nom, pp.projet_id
		ORDER BY pg.nom, pp.nom
SELECT distinct pp.*, pg.nom AS groupe_nom
		FROM planning_projet pp
		LEFT JOIN planning_periode pd ON pp.projet_id = pd.projet_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe AS pg ON pp.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id WHERE (
			(pd.date_debut <= '2019-09-19'
			AND pd.date_fin >= '2019-09-19')
			OR
			(pd.date_debut <= '2019-11-19'
			AND pd.date_debut >= '2019-09-19')
			)
			AND planning_projet.projet_id != 'timetable'	GROUP BY pp.nom, pp.projet_id
			ORDER BY pg.nom, pp.nom
SELECT distinct pp.*, pg.nom AS groupe_nom
		FROM planning_projet pp
		LEFT JOIN planning_periode pd ON pp.projet_id = pd.projet_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe AS pg ON pp.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id WHERE (
			(pd.date_debut <= '2019-09-19'
			AND pd.date_fin >= '2019-09-19')
			OR
			(pd.date_debut <= '2019-11-19'
			AND pd.date_debut >= '2019-09-19')
			)
			AND planning_projet.projet_id != 'timetable' AND planning_projet.projet_id != 'holiday'	GROUP BY pp.nom, pp.projet_id
			ORDER BY pg.nom, pp.nom

		FROM planning_projet pp
		LEFT JOIN planning_periode pd ON pp.projet_id = pd.projet_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe AS pg ON pp.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id WHERE (

			AND pd.date_fin >= '2019-09-19')
			OR
			(pd.date_debut <= '2019-11-19'
			AND pd.date_debut >= '2019-09-19')
			AND planning_periode.projet_id != 'holiday')
				GROUP BY pp.nom, pp.projet_id
			ORDER BY pg.nom, pp.nom

		FROM planning_projet pp
		LEFT JOIN planning_periode pd ON pp.projet_id = pd.projet_id

SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE AND planning_projet.projet_id != 'holiday' AND planning_projet.projet_id != 'timetable' and planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-02' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-09-02')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-11-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-09-02')
			)
SELECT planning_periode.*,planning_projet.statut, planning_status.nom as status_nom,  planning_status.barre as statut_barre,planning_status.gras as statut_gras,planning_status.italique as statut_italique,planning_status.souligne as statut_souligne, planning_status.couleur as statut_couleur,planning_status.pourcentage as statut_pourcentage, pu.nom as user_nom, pu.couleur as user_couleur,
		planning_projet.nom as projet_nom, planning_projet.couleur as projet_couleur, pg.nom AS groupe_nom,  pu.*, pug.nom AS team_nom,
		pl.nom as lieu_nom, pr.nom as ressource_nom, planning_projet.charge as charge, planning_projet.createur_id AS projet_createur_id,
		puc.nom AS nom_createur, pum.nom AS nom_modifier,
		CASE 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'AM' THEN '08:00:00;08:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'PM' THEN '14:00:00;14:01:00' 
		   WHEN planning_periode.duree_details = 'duree' THEN NULL    
		   ELSE planning_periode.duree_details 
		END AS tri_heures_taches
		FROM planning_periode
		INNER JOIN planning_projet on planning_projet.projet_id = planning_periode.projet_id
		INNER JOIN planning_status on planning_status.status_id = planning_periode.statut_tache
		INNER JOIN planning_user as pu on planning_periode.user_id = pu.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as puc on planning_periode.createur_id = puc.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user as pum on planning_periode.modifier_id = pum.user_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_user_groupe as pug on pu.user_groupe_id = pug.user_groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_groupe as pg on planning_projet.groupe_id = pg.groupe_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_lieu as pl on planning_periode.lieu_id = pl.lieu_id
		LEFT JOIN planning_ressource as pr on planning_periode.ressource_id = pr.ressource_id	WHERE AND planning_projet.projet_id != 'holiday' AND planning_projet.projet_id != 'timetable' and planning_periode.projet_id = planning_projet.projet_id and (
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-09-02' AND planning_periode.date_fin >= '2019-09-02')
			OR
			(planning_periode.date_debut <= '2019-11-30' AND planning_periode.date_debut >= '2019-09-02')
			) ORDER by lieu_nom ASC
